Combine cabbage, onions, carrot, salt and 1/2 cup SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener in a large bowl. Set aside. Whisk together the remaining 1/2 cup SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, oil, vinegar, dry mustard, and celery seeds in a small saucepan; bring mixture to a boil over medium-high heat. Pour hot mixture over cabbage mixture, tossing to coat. Cover and chill one-hour or overnight.